WEBVTT

00:02.385 --> 00:03.708
So do you think you can help me?

00:03.917 --> 00:06.164
I'd like very much to help you,

00:06.206 --> 00:07.164
and I think I can.

00:07.206 --> 00:08.874
Did you kill Bob Paris?

00:08.916 --> 00:10.164
What's your endgame here?

00:10.206 --> 00:13.164
$3 million.

00:13.206 --> 00:15.164
<i>Every safety deposit
box requires two keys.</i>

00:15.206 --> 00:16.875
<i>The bank has one.</i>

00:17.029 --> 00:18.987
<i>The box renter holds on to the other.</i>

00:19.160 --> 00:20.118
What do you want?

00:20.161 --> 00:21.985
