00:24.043 --> 00:24.917
You want to kill him?

00:24.960 --> 00:26.416
Is that what you want?

00:26.458 --> 00:28.416
<i>I just black out and...</i>

00:28.458 --> 00:30.918
<i>And maybe because I'm
crazy or something.</i>

00:30.960 --> 00:32.415
<i>I-I don't know.</i>

00:32.458 --> 00:34.416
What do you think about Norman?

00:34.458 --> 00:36.416
You want to know what's
really wrong with Norman,

00:36.458 --> 00:38.416
you should talk to the
person who knows him best.

00:38.458 --> 00:40.416
- And that's you?
- Of course it is.

00:40.458 --> 00:41.918
I'm his mother.

