- Okay. See you.

02:07.588 --> 02:08.588
Alex.

02:12.235 --> 02:14.193
It's funny, you and I, isn't it?

02:14.235 --> 02:17.193
<i>(TENDER PIANO MUSIC)</i>

02:17.235 --> 02:20.194
That we're here and... And we're happy,

02:20.236 --> 02:23.945
that after everything, we've made it.

02:26.235 --> 02:28.695
And you're going off to
work and kissing me,

02:28.737 --> 02:30.193
and it's like I'm watching a movie,

02:30.235 --> 02:32.695
but it's not a movie.

02:46.737 --> 02:49.193
It's not a movie.

02:49.235 --> 02:50.193
Don't screw it up.

02:50.235 --> 02:54.193
(LAUGHS)

